---
title: Seared Chicken & Warm Roast Cauliflower Salad with Indian Coconut Dressing
description: We've stepped up every element of this sublime salad, from roasted veggies with a pop of brown mustard seeds to tangy pickled onion and a lip-smackingly good coconut dressing, infused with mild Indian spices.
